title: The Kid with the Stick
description: Think Fast, Tina has an update about meeting her new boyfriend's family, Weekend X Factor, Monday Motivation, we talk to Jeff Wagner from WCCO about an old video of Prince that was dug up from when he was 11, things get hurtful during Cold Reading Jokes, we get bored and play with the equipment, and more!
